OL,3,CUse of heritage names for ITV regional
OL,4,Cnews programmes: further comment
OL,6,GSome may have been surprised to read
OL,7,Gmy argument that ITV should drop the
OL,8,Guse of legacy brands in the English
OL,9,Gregions.
OL,11,FIt may seem like an odd argument to
OL,12,Fmake for someone who cares about the
OL,13,Frich heritage of broadcasting.
OL,15,FOf course, arguments are just that `
OL,16,Farguments. Other people can take the
OL,17,Fopposite view and nobody is right or
OL,18,Fwrong.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/9
