OL,3,CUse of heritage names for ITV regional
OL,4,Cnews programmes: further comment
OL,6,FMy belief that a rebranding should be
OL,7,Fconsidered is rooted in a passionate
OL,8,Fconcern for regional news provision
OL,9,Fitself.
OL,11,FIt is one of ITV's key legal
OL,12,Fobligations. High quality regional
OL,13,Fnews on C3 provides competition for
OL,14,Fthe BBC, choice for the public and
OL,15,Fplurality in a democracy.
OL,17,FWith TV ratings declining, it is
OL,18,Fimportant to make sure high quality,
OL,19,Freputable journalism is available
OL,20,Fonline too.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/9
