OL,3,CUse of heritage names for ITV regional
OL,4,Cnews programmes: further comment
OL,6,FThis is absolutely vital to contain
OL,7,Fthe scourge of fake news and ensure
OL,8,Fpeople continue to hear a wide range
OL,9,Fof views and opinions ` not just those
OL,10,Fthey agree with.
OL,12,FSo what has any of this got to do with
OL,13,Flegacy brands?
OL,15,FThe clue is in the word legacy.
OL,16,FRegional news is too important to
OL,17,Ftreat as a legacy.
