OL,3,CUse of heritage names for ITV regional
OL,4,Cnews programmes: further comment
OL,6,FHistorically English TV regions
OL,7,Freflected transmitter coverage areas `
OL,8,Fnot existing political or cultural
OL,9,Fentities. Where the two combined it
OL,10,Fwas fortuitous.
OL,12,FHowever when ITV was a commercial
OL,13,Fmonopoly, TV regions helped to forge
OL,14,Fan additional identity. Which TV
OL,15,Fregion you lived in mattered ` even if
OL,16,Fyou did not watch much TV or preferred
OL,17,Fthe BBC.
OL,19,FFranchise changes ` for good or ill `
OL,20,Falso mattered.
OL,22,FNone of this is relevant today though.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/9
