OL,3,CUse of heritage names for ITV regional
OL,4,Cnews programmes: further comment
OL,6,FITV is one company ` the regional
OL,7,Flicences are held by ITV Broadcasting
OL,8,FLtd not, say, ITV Granada or ITV
OL,9,FMeridian.
OL,11,FThe EPG only lists ITV 1 and ITV 1 HD.
OL,13,FMany TV guides no longer routinely
OL,14,Facknowledge English regions ` except
OL,15,Fon the days ITV's monthly regional
OL,16,Fpolitical programmes are shown.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/9
