OL,3,CUse of heritage names for ITV regional
OL,4,Cnews programmes: further comment
OL,6,FAs far as I know, only TV Times, the
OL,7,FDaily Mirror and the Daily Express
OL,8,Fstill publish blank columns which
OL,9,Factively list the regions then say
OL,10,Fthere are no variations. This too is a
OL,11,Flegacy which could well go in the next
OL,12,Frevamp. An English viewer has no
OL,13,Freason to presume their local ITV 1
OL,14,Fschedule will be different to the main
OL,15,Fone.
OL,17,FWith all those factors in mind, it
OL,18,Fwould be fascinating to know just how
OL,19,Fmuch brand recognition the English
OL,20,Fregional names still enjoy.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/9
