OL,3,CUse of heritage names for ITV regional
OL,4,Cnews programmes: further comment
OL,6,FIf you moved to a different part of
OL,7,Fthe country would you immediately know
OL,8,Fwhich TV region you were in? I suspect
OL,9,Fmany would not.
OL,11,FWith all this in mind, I believe
OL,12,Freconsidering brand names to ensure
OL,13,Fthere is an explicit, contemporary
OL,14,Fconnection between the regional news
OL,15,Ftitles and the areas they serve would
OL,16,Fbe a positive move.
OL,18,FIt could also make online navigation
OL,19,Feasier and more relevant.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/9
