OL,3,CUse of heritage names for ITV regional
OL,4,Cnews programmes: further comment
OL,6,FAn old brand name is not a bad thing
OL,7,Fwhen it is still relevant. Many of the
OL,8,FBBC's English regional news titles
OL,9,Fdate from the 1960s. But with the
OL,10,Fexception of Spotlight they all
OL,11,Fexplicitly refer to the broad region
OL,12,Fthey serve, not a bygone corporate
OL,13,Fname.
OL,15,FCrucially the BBC does not apply those
OL,16,Fprogramme brands to its website.
OL,18,FITV could be accused of treating its
OL,19,Fregional names with a certain benign
OL,20,Fneglect ` it isn't building the
OL,21,Fregional brands but it is not killing
OL,22,Fthem either.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/9
