OL,3,CUse of heritage names for ITV regional
OL,4,Cnews programmes: further comment
OL,6,FHowever that is not a fair reflection
OL,7,Fon the company's attitude to the
OL,8,Fregional news services ` since 2013 it
OL,9,Fhas improved and maintained them.
OL,11,FOthers may legitimately believe
OL,12,Fheritage names have a powerful
OL,13,Fresonance and should stay.
OL,15,FMy own view is that names should
OL,16,Freflect present realities.
OL,18,FBut all of this is worthy of
OL,19,Fdiscussion.
